    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per the MRL 2 scoping decision, which is consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is judged credible for its intended use: identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is supported by the validation evidence.",
